premise_source_doc_sentence: Judith Quiney  (  baptised 2 February 1585 -- 9 February 1662  )  , née Shakespeare , was the younger daughter of William Shakespeare and Anne Hathaway and the fraternal twin of Shakespeare 's only son Hamnet Shakespeare .
